{"tid":1180193,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jackson為好友做伴郎被玩　男男咀嘴慘遭伸脷","createTime":"2019-05-31T15:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T22:40:03.000Z","uid":46435,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"342c85fa79d116387af8fbe8a53bff1e2739b3ed","tid":1180193,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"GOT7的Jackson為由細玩到大的好友Henry當伴郎，穿上筆挺帥氣西裝跟兄弟團陪住新郎去接新娘已搶晒鏡，但幾靚仔都無情講，與兄弟團代新郎接下姊妹團派的「嘴對嘴傳花瓣」任務時，花瓣跌下，男男就咀上了，現場隨即起哄，Jackson無奈搖頭：「你咀還咀，做乜伸脷呀？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190529_EN_%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190529_EN_%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%2588%25BE4.jpg&h=c9157209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190529_EN_%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190529_EN_%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%2588%25BE3.jpg&h=c3d07b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190529_EN_%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190529_EN_%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%2588%25BE7.jpg&h=479a75ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，Jackson不單百忙抽空做伴郎，還幫好兄弟策劃，又帶自己的化妝師到場，就是為了給Henry做最靚仔的新郎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/05/20190529_EN_%E7%8E%8B%E5%98%89%E7%88%BE6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F05%2F20190529_EN_%25E7%258E%258B%25E5%2598%2589%25E7%2588%25BE6.jpg&h=8b